EmailTemplate.name: Tax forms for Solar Credits
EmailTemplate.subject: TAX FORMS FOR SOLAR CREDITS
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hello
Attached to this email are the State and Federal Tax forms that you or your accountant will need to complete in order to take advantage of the solar tax credits.
On both forms, you will need to include the cost of your solar system On Form #1350 you do NOT need to fill in any of the three checkboxes at the top of the page.
Please call the Palmetto Customer Care Department, or consult your CPA if you have any further questions about your tax forms.
Sincerely,
Palmetto Customer Care Team customer.care@palmetto.com Phone: 855-339-1831 Office: 843-720-1844
